        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1.0</title>
            <sparkle:version>2</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2026 22:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in Version 1.1.0</h2>
                
                <h3>New Features</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Video Ads</strong> - Ads now support YouTube videos (including Shorts) with auto-loop</li>
                    <li><strong>GIF Ads</strong> - Animated GIF support with smooth looping</li>
                    <li><strong>Direct Video Files</strong> - MP4 video file support for ads</li>
                    <li><strong>Always-Visible Titles</strong> - Ad titles now displayed with transparent overlay</li>
                </ul>
                
                <h3>Improvements</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Privacy-enhanced YouTube embedding (youtube-nocookie.com)</li>
                    <li>Minimised YouTube branding where possible</li>
                    <li>Improved admin dashboard with side-by-side form layout</li>
                    <li>Video preview in admin dashboard</li>
                </ul>
                
                <h3>Technical</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Added VideoPlayerView, YouTubeWebView, GIFWebView components</li>
                    <li>Updated Supabase function to support video ads</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            
